# Football Stats Collector

## Description
A Python script that collects football statistics from two sources:
- Historical data from CSV (International Football Results)
- Live data from Football-Data.org API

## What it does
- Loads and cleans historical goalscorers and results data
- Fetches live matches from API
- Merges both sources into one unified dataset
- Generates a summary report

## How to run
pip install pandas requests
python collector.py

